msContents.summary: Collections of hymns on the Law, the Cross, and for the cycle of the year with a homily on silence.

name.#text: J. Rendel Harris Collection (Quaker & Special Collections, Haverford College)

supportDesc.extent: 178 leaves : 163 x 110 (130 x 80) mm bound to 168 x 113 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Modern foliation in pencil added, upper left recto.

decoNote: Rubrications in red; text division decoration in red and black (f. 24v).

binding.p: Red leather with blind tooled frame of double lines with three sets of double lines intersecting in the center.

origin.p: Copy completed by ʼEramyā, possibly in the 19th century (f. 85r).

history.provenance: Formerly owned by J. Rendel Harris.
